01:08:38.670 --> 01:08:39.645
- Sure.

01:08:39.645 --> 01:08:41.720
- Like, if you
enjoy football, you

01:08:41.720 --> 01:08:46.130
are witnessing the
destruction of young men.

01:08:46.130 --> 01:08:47.750
That's what we're doing.

01:08:47.750 --> 01:08:51.330
I hope all of you guys
don't leave right now.

01:08:51.330 --> 01:08:53.330
But every time I
watch a football game,

01:08:53.330 --> 01:08:55.550
I literally think,
